channel.title: Farming on Allstar-Scape V2
channel.description: Farming doesn't work on Allstar-Scape V2 for some reason. It has this when you mouse over the farming icon [IMG]http://i707.photobucket.com/albums/ww76/Jakesta96/farmprob.jpg[/img] You can use the seeds with the bucket and Guide the patches and stuff, it's supposed to add XP to farming but it doesn't. And it's probably because of that thing saying Next level at: -1. What do you suggest I do besides switch sources.
